Dialogs.Dialog: You turned off the power without saving, right? It's against the rules.
Did you turn off the power without saving? Why are you doing something so terrible?
You turned off the power without saving, right? It's a good prospect.
You turned off the power without saving again... I went to all this trouble to forgive you.
You turned off the power without saving again... I was careful the other day.
Did you turn off the power without saving again? Didn't you hear my request?
You know why I'm angry right? You turned off the power without saving, right?
You turned off the power without saving many times... It's not good it it's on purpose.
You turned off the power without saving, how many times have you done this? This is the limit.
Say "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me". Say it with all your heart.
The way to apologize is saying "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me". Then... I'll believe in you.
Until you say "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me", I won't forgive you, understand?
"I won't do it anymore, please forgive me"... Don't make me repeat it again.
Listen well. "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me".
"I won't do it anymore, please forgive me". Can you say it?
Say it more properly. Because it's important.
I'm sorry, I didn't get that. One more time, okay?
I'm not convinced with just that. Clearly, one more time.
I can believe that... Yes, I forgive you.
Eh... sly. You know, I forgive you...
Ah... It's different from what I asked... It's not right... But, I forgive you.
Oh, already... I can't help it.
I beg of you. Don't do anything terrible anymore.
Well then, this story is over. Right?
Don't let me down any more...
If you keep silent, you won't anything...
You turned off the power without saving again... Quit that already!
You turned off the power without saving again... Can you remember what I told you?
I know it, you turned off the power without saving again.
If you want me to forgive you... "I love Manaka the most". Now, say it.
Can you say "I love Manaka the most"? Then I will too...
"I love Manaka the most". I can't forgive you unless you tell me that.
No way, are you going to keep quiet all the time?
Why don't you tell me anything?
I'll know even if you cheat. One more time.
I want you to say it properly. Can you try again?
Say it clearly. One more time.
I don't want to hear that.
Don't you want to say that much?
I don't really understand what you are saying...
I'm glad... I wonder what would you do if I didn't told you.
But it's not enough. Say "I like you" 3 times.
Next... Say "I like you" 3 times. Then I'll accept it.
Then, if you say "I like you" 3 times, I'll really forgive you.
I'll get angrier next time, okay?
Don't you want to make up?
You know what I mean, right?
I don't want you to tell me anything silly...
Fufu, I made you say it.
Yes... let me tell you, but... I'm shy.
Well then, let's make up again. No doing this anymore, okay? It's an important memory.
Finally, remember it. Even if something seems unpleasant, it's a memory of us.
Promise you'll never do this again. All good and bad things are part of our memories.
If you're really reflecting on it... I want you to say a lot of words of love to prove you're serious.
The word I want you to say is "I love you".
Um... I would you to say "I'm sorry" a lot, okay?
Well then... Say "I will never cheat".
Hmm... My feelings can't reach you.
Yes. I was able to convey your feelings.
Nice♪ You set a new record!
If you're reflecting on it, express those feelings of reflection.
Do your best, do your best~.
I have to write it carefully.
I'm really loving it. It was good♪
Wow, you've reached a new record!
If you've reflected on it, can you stare at my eyes? If you can't then you're not honest.
Just me... Just look at me.
Incredible! You have set a new record♪
It's already a give-up. You're going to reflect on it, aren't you?
Okay... I'll forgive you this time.
